        comparison_summary: '<p>Warp compares directly to legacy terminal emulators like iTerm2 on macOS, or the default Terminal application. While iTerm2 offers deep, complex customization for power users, Warp emphasizes a modernized data-entry experience and assistive AI, making it more accessible and structurally different from traditional CLI workflows.</p>'
