        best_for: ['Small business owners requiring rapid, functional web deployments', 'Freelancers and consultants building basic portfolio endpoints', 'Users seeking an all-in-one solution for hosting, design, and generation'],
        pros: ['Lowers the barrier to entry significantly by constructing a functional baseline structure rather than forcing a start from a blank page', 'The integration of business widgets (like bookings or simple stores) into the generated output is practically useful', 'Operates within the established, widely supported Wix ecosystem, ensuring ongoing maintenance and hosting reliability'],
