        comparison_summary: '<p>Wix AI operates in the website builder sector alongside Squarespace and Shopify, as well as AI-specific builders like Framer or Unicorn Platform. While Framer targets advanced designers seeking high-control interactions, Wix focuses on business practicality, providing a highly automated, accessible pipeline for non-technical retail or service-based users.</p>'
