        pros: ['Provides immediate, 24/7 access to established CBT exercises without requiring scheduled clinical appointments', 'The strict reliance on structured, clinical scripts prevents unpredictable or harmful AI hallucinations', 'The conversational interface encourages higher longitudinal adherence compared to standard static self-help workbooks'],
        cons: ['It is fundamentally not a replacement for professional human psychiatric or psychological intervention for severe clinical diagnoses', 'The constrained, scripted nature of the interactions can feel repetitive or inflexible during highly nuanced distress', 'It struggles to parse highly complex, multi-layered human emotional context, operating optimally only within defined parameters'],
